This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with head and body pose estimation. The use of Gaussian process regression and matrix completion also suggests that it could belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the use of multimodal sensor data could place it in the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category, while the focus on conversational interaction suggests it could also belong to the human-computer interaction (cs.HC) sub-category.
